dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Brown County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Brown County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'Brown_Hydro_2020_Line' and 'Brown_Hydro_2020_Poly'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://www.browncountywi.gov/departments/planning-and-land-services/land-information-office/]
